data.description: Cute as can be home in downtown Polson.  This 3 bedroom 1 bath home with detached double garage is central to all amenities in Polson.  Enjoy being just blocks from beaches, shopping, dining, gyms, and summer festivals.  Mature trees provide beauty and shade, and the fenced yard makes it easy to move right in with critters.  Home is older but has been well maintained.  Warmth and character all in a fantastic location!  Call the Smith Team at 406 261 0641, or your real estate professional, for additional information.
